%H A362979 Pontus von Brömssen, <a href="/A362979/b362979.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 3..19703</a> (first 198 antidiagonals)
%e A362979 Corner:
%e A362979   n=3:    7    11    13    19    37   41     67    73    97
%e A362979   n=4:   23    29    43    53    71   83     89   101   113
